  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nThe `Collation` object currently uses a stateful and mutation based mechanism for storing the total transaction fee.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/jannikluhn/py-evm/blob/65d7b24d718b1aa1238ba72a385d16baa93498e7/evm/vm/forks/sharding/collations.py#L29\r\n\r\nIt would be better if we can find a way to track that value and expose it in the appropriate place(s) in a more explicit way.\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nNeed to investigate.",
